 || {{right|5.55}}\n| {{right|2,475}}   || {{right|18.88}}\n| {{right|183}}     || {{right|1.40}}\n| {{right|13,108}}\n|-\n| [[Andrijevica]]\n| {{right|0}}       || {{right|0.00}}\n| {{right|3,137}}   || {{right|61.86}}\n| {{right|1,646}}   || {{right|32.46}}\n| {{right|7}}       || {{right|0.14}}\n| {{right|1}}       || {{right|0.02}}\n| {{right|280}}     || {{right|5.52}}\n| {{right|5,071}}\n|-\n! Sand\u017eak\n| {{right|189,186}} || {{right|48.42}}\n| {{right|132,335}} || {{right|33.86}}\n| {{right|28,250}}  || {{right|7.23}}\n| {{right|23,900}}  || {{right|6.12}}\n| {{right|4,062}}   || {{right|1.04}}\n| {{right|13,004}}  || {{right|3.33}}\n| {{right|390,737}}\n|-\n| colspan=\"14\" | <center>2011 census</center>\n|}\n\n==Gallery==\n<gallery>\nImage:Novi Pazar02.JPG|[[Novi Pazar]]\nImage:BedemNP.jpg| A wall built during the [[Ottoman Empire|Ottoman]] period in [[Novi Pazar]]\nImage:Nova Varos 30's.jpg|[[Nova Varo\u0161]] in 1930's\nImage:Kucanska_dzamija.jpg|[[Ku\u010danska Mosque]], [[Ro\u017eaje]] from 1830.\nImage:Nova Varos Center 2004.JPG|[[Nova Varo\u0161]] Centre in 2004\nImage:Pljevlja Mosque 1.JPG|Husein-pasha's mosque, [[Pljevlja]]\nImage:Crkva Svetih apostola Petra i Pavla (Petrova crkva), Novi Pazar, Srbija.jpg|[[Church of the Holy Apostles Peter and Paul, Ras]] near [[Novi Pazar]], 8-9th century\nImage:Stari Ras.jpg|[[Stari Ras]] fortress near [[Novi Pazar]], 8th century\nImage:\u0110ur\u0111evi stupovi, November 2005.jpg|[[\u0110ur\u0111evi Stupovi]] monastery, near [[Novi Pazar]], 12th century\nImage:Meister von Mileseva 001.jpg|[[White Angel]], fresco from [[Mile\u0161eva monastery]] near [[Prijepolje]], c. 1235\nImage:Manastir Sopocani.jpg|[[Sopo\u0107ani]] monastery, 13th century\n</gallery>\n\n==See also==\n* [[Bosniaks]]\n* [[Bosniaks of Serbia]]\n* [[Bosniaks of Montenegro]]\n* [[Flag of Sand\u017eak]]\n* [[Geography of Serbia]]\n* [[Geography of Montenegro]]\n\n== References ==\n\n=== Notes ===\n\n{{reflist}}\n\n=== Sources ===\n\n{{refbegin